document_data.name: Tiatha Hawksong
document_data.mainbody: '''Tiatha Hawksong''' was the leader of the [[moon elf]] house [[House Hawksong|Hawksong]].
document_data.History: Tiatha disappeared around [[1357 DR]], but members of her house believed her to still be alive in [[1367 DR]].
document_data.Rumors and legends: It was rumored she possessed the ''[[Gem of Clarata]]''.
